## Q12 — Ibadi position on jinn

### (a) Nature of jinn — the *jism laṭīf* doctrine

**Evidence.** The most precise verbatim retrieval comes from a published fatwa of the current Mufti of Oman, **Aḥmad b. Ḥamad al-Khalīlī**, transcribed in *al-Rūʾyā* (Oman daily, 28 May 2025):

